Sentencas: Ferritic stainless steel (FSS) is an appropriate material to be used in solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) interconnect.
Titulo: Effect of W and Ti addition on oxidation behavior and area-specific resistance of Fe-22Cr-0.5Mn ferritic stainless steel for SOFCs interconnect

Sentencas: Chromium in FSS evaporates at high temperature and it is deposited on the cathode surface of SOFC and makes the cell poisonous.
Titulo: Effect of W and Ti addition on oxidation behavior and area-specific resistance of Fe-22Cr-0.5Mn ferritic stainless steel for SOFCs interconnect

Sentencas: So the present study, the effect of W and Ti addition on oxidation behavior, electrical property and Cr evaporation resistance were discussed in terms of microstructure property of the oxide scale by using SEM analysis.
Titulo: Effect of W and Ti addition on oxidation behavior and area-specific resistance of Fe-22Cr-0.5Mn ferritic stainless steel for SOFCs interconnect

Sentencas: W and Ti addition reduce the oxidation rate, Cr evaporation rate and area-specific resistance of the FSS.
Titulo: Effect of W and Ti addition on oxidation behavior and area-specific resistance of Fe-22Cr-0.5Mn ferritic stainless steel for SOFCs interconnect

Sentencas: Presence of W in this steel formed chi (chi) phase in scale/alloy interface and prevented the diffusion of cation to the oxide scale.
Titulo: Effect of W and Ti addition on oxidation behavior and area-specific resistance of Fe-22Cr-0.5Mn ferritic stainless steel for SOFCs interconnect

Sentencas: It is also a barrier for the influence of the oxygen anion to the inward of the FSS.
Titulo: Effect of W and Ti addition on oxidation behavior and area-specific resistance of Fe-22Cr-0.5Mn ferritic stainless steel for SOFCs interconnect

Sentencas: The presence of high amount of W and low amount of Ti were effective in improving oxidation and electrical conductivity.
Titulo: Effect of W and Ti addition on oxidation behavior and area-specific resistance of Fe-22Cr-0.5Mn ferritic stainless steel for SOFCs interconnect

Sentencas: However, to enhance the Cr evaporation resistance, high Ti content is required.
